name: Cassini
body:
### Intro

Cassini is an Software Defined Networking application developed at the University of Washington


### Network Access Control  


### Getting Started
```
$ git clone http://github.com/chrissmall22/cassini
```

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Cassini? Check out the wiki and issues in Github or send a message to the Cassini user mailing list cassini-user@googlegroups.com
